    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1936-02-08T19:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1936-02-08T19:00:00-05:00" n="41"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d41">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">724.34119/374: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Chargé in Bolivia</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Muccio</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">La Paz</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1936-02-08T20:00:00-04:00"
                            >February 8, 1936—8 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received 9 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>4. Bolivian Congress has just approved Buenos Aires protocol by joint Senate,
                    Chamber of Deputies unanimous vote. Repeated to Buenos Aires.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Muccio</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
